SetInCountry: Portugal
Category: A leap into the unknown
AuthorName: Karin Reichow
AuthorCountry: United States of America
Text: "Went to Portugal with the whole family for a surfing vacation HOWEVER ended\
  \ up having the best time for completely different reason , the climate , the food,\
  \ the markets , everything just seemed like such a different t experience and So\
  \ much fun. We met amazing people on the beaches , we made great friends with a\
  \ hostel/surfing  school of English lads , found great restaurants \nand fish markets\
  \ and unbelievable local grown foods and vegetables  like hot peppers . Also a great\
  \ international community of surfers , restaurants and bars lots of coffee shops\
  \ and the most amazing sea kayaking ever experienced through grottos and under huge\
  \ caves in beautiful blue green waters with amazing views"
